    <title><literal>SendImage()</literal></title>

    <indexterm significance="preferred">
      <primary>Dialplan Applications</primary>

      <secondary><code>SendImage()</code></secondary>
    </indexterm>

    <simpara>Sends an image file to the channel.</simpara>

    <synopsis><command>SendImage(<replaceable>filename</replaceable>[,<replaceable>options</replaceable>])</command></synopsis>

    <simpara>Sends an image file to the channel. If images are supported and
    the transmission fails, the application hangs up; otherwise it continues
    on the next priority. If option <code>j</code> is set, the application
    jumps to priority <replaceable>n</replaceable>+101, if it
    exists.</simpara>

    <simpara>Returns 0 on successful transmission of the image or if the
    channel does not support images, otherwise returns -1. Sets the channel
    variable <code>SENDIMAGESTATUS</code> to <code>OK</code> or
    <code>NOSUPPORT</code>.</simpara>

    <programlisting>exten =&gt; 123,1,SendImage(logo.jpg)</programlisting>

